ReviewText: As an avid walker I have used many times with my flask of water. Excellent flavour, so easy to use. Fresh tasting coffee when you really need one during or after a hike. I prefer the added sugar as it gives me an energy boost to go the extra mile!

Title: Compact convenient coffee

ReviewText: first in the morning is my favorite coffee from Nescafe 3 in 1......what can I say ...its delicious and I enjoy this lovely coffee..its a good start of the day
Title: me and my nescafe

ReviewText: I work in a office and quite frankly was sick of going to the canteen to make myself a well deserved coffee and discovering that my milk had been used on someone else's cereal and my jar of nescafe had mysteriously emptied itself so I decided to give the 3 in 1 sachets ago. I was sceptical after having powder milk incidents in the past but from the first time I poured the water and used the 3 in 1 sachets I was hooked tastes just like nescafe with fresh milk no need to worry about the office politics and milk shortage! And the sachets are easily stored in my handbag safe from mysteriously going walkabouts!
Title: Hassle free cuppa

ReviewText: I sampled this product whilst at a hotel in London. Really surprised at the smooth blend when mixed with boiling water at the time. The sweetness and coffee taste came bubbling through to provide a most pleasing refreshment I have had for a long time. Would recommend this for a quick cuppa!!Well done Nescafe!
Title: Excellent on the go Quickie!

ReviewText: I always keep a pack of these in, just in case I run out of milk, usually a pack of 5, I was surprised to see a pack of 10 in asda couple of weeks ago so had to get one. I even keep two in the car as my youngest and girlfriend dont keep coffee in, this way I take my own
Title: My emergency stock

ReviewText: I drink around four or five cups of 3 in 1 every day. It's simply quick to make and has a nice taste. It doesn't taste harsh or bitter like some other coffees. I really enjoy it and would recommend it to anyone who is in need of a quick coffee when on the go.
